<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />說起這座島，<delay20 />這裡充滿了自然景觀，<delay20 /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />
真的很振奮人心耶！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我每天都<delay8 />感到興奮不已──！！<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像是抓蟲或捕魚啊、<delay8 />鍛鍊臂力、<delay20 />
環島慢跑，跑到腿部痠痛啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗚喔──！<delay8 />太多想做的事啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在島嶼上的生活<delay20 />
總會給人一種野外求生的印象，<delay frames="30" />
但其實並不是這樣啦。<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像我<delay8 />就比較<delay8 />期待<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能跟巨大的<delay8 />敵人戰鬥──！<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦？<delay8 />只有我這麼想嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />直到認識你之前，<delay20 />
我一直以為這世界上<delay8 />沒有人比我厲害，<pageBreak /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但沒想到<delay8 />竟然能在這座島上<delay20 />
與我最棒的好對手一同生活──！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘿嘿，其實我<delay8 />挺開心的喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>